it does to your medical license,

212
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:33,375
but I'm thinking
it can't be good.

213
00:10:33,417 --> 00:10:36,542
I don't want you.

214
00:10:36,583 --> 00:10:41,291
Tell me where her son is,
I let you go.

215
00:10:43,083 --> 00:10:46,000
