762
00:38:44,083 --> 00:38:45,709
Nothing.

763
00:38:45,750 --> 00:38:49,291
It's just, you wouldn't
know it to look at you,

764
00:38:49,333 --> 00:38:51,500
that you care.

765
00:38:51,542 --> 00:38:53,208
♪♪♪

